{"tid":10120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致admin, 改名提議","createTime":"2016-11-28T22:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T05:11:29.000Z","uid":11747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3781f53c5d13db099c99f3368e67c2151be246","tid":10120,"uid":11747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T22:07:20.000Z","msg":"其實見到好多巴打咁緊張LIHKG, 特別係d 建議上。 真係好開心有一個新嘅地方可以自由討論，避開打手，五毛。 <br />\n<br />\n係改名方面，小弟有d 愚見，希望admin 及各巴打可加入考慮。 而考慮要點如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 可增加討論區收入，令會員收費空間可下調，吸引更多會員加入。 <br />\n2. 發揮推廣角色，幫助更多有特色嘅地方，節目，企業或活動<br />\n<br />\n方式：<br />\n如足球隊出售球場冠名權，以三個月，半年為期。 一來已達廣角宣傳效用，二來有穩定收入，可補貼收費會員費用，三來可減少討論區內廣告數量，吸引更多非付費oa員。 <br />\n<br />\n並無意引起罵戰，希望admin 及各巴打自由討論及考慮建議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b099c9d5b8ea4685f1b261fc06e3c0332984b4","tid":10120,"uid":27890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T22:10:01.000Z","msg":"事鳩但啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 你個建議同改名有咩關係？"},{"pid":"d6e0c17ea966ab65289b24907550f4045098b48a","tid":10120,"uid":11747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T22:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事鳩但啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 你個建議同改名有咩關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改名個意思係幫LIHKG 改番個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而與其改一個名，可考慮以冠名方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3f14c6de8dcab6aa558bd972b64fd5abae22e2","tid":10120,"uid":27890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T22:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改名個意思係幫LIHKG 改番個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而與其改一個名，可考慮以冠名方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOh 即係搵sponsor？"},{"pid":"b936044665eeccd998422a6f5e00a88dd0a3b370","tid":10120,"uid":11747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T22:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改名個意思係幫LIHKG 改番個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而與其改一個名，可考慮以冠名方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOh 即係搵sponsor？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，而只係冠名，而不能干預全何討論內容"},{"pid":"da2d4eb5018bda58d1cd4c0248db35e007f06dc6","tid":10120,"uid":27890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T22:33:40.000Z","msg":"但依度既admin都係IT人<br />\n開壇幾日 未必咁快有人負責涉外喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但長遠計係幾好既建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d4db05835b07fa317b75ec78597d52d28a422f","tid":10120,"uid":11747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T22:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但依度既admin都係IT人<br />\n開壇幾日 未必咁快有人負責涉外喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但長遠計係幾好既建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以可以先討論，再準備。 作為中長遠計劃。 而咁多類型廣告方式，冠名對用戶嘅影響無咁大。"},{"pid":"ec9d81a0cd8b292cac814b87655eb8ff33f55af3","tid":10120,"uid":1300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:14:17.000Z","msg":"不如叫鳩登"},{"pid":"ede2e01b7e1d96fee8ff71c27a186807d1828899","tid":10120,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如叫鳩登</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就真係碌鳩喇<br />\n<br />\nlihkg 遲d 取代埋高登，d 記者上黎拎料點報阿？"},{"pid":"f89f860505472f79632c33fde454ddc7aabefb05","tid":10120,"uid":11747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}